'''Light and Shadow''' was a story written for the ''[[Star Wars Adventure Journal]]'' by [[Paul Danner]]. It was never published, but was later released on the Internet. It was set in the time of the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]] and dealt with a [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]] young girl helping a fallen [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] come to terms with himself.

